column5: It looks like you spent it well!!! Great looking fall meal.
Im hungry again. That,s a sweet looking dinner.
Looks awesome. You had me at chestnut stuffing.  I'm drooling already for my wife's chestnut sausage stuffing  tomorrow when the whole clan comes over!!!

Low down on the chestnut sausage stuffing.  How is it made? Busy with prep now Brian..then company. I'll send you the recipe later...or tomorrow.  If I forget shoot me a PM. Debbe got this recipe 2-3 years ago. She already made the best stuffing I have ever had but this is even better. It never goes in the bird either so you can have it as a side dish whenever you want   Which we do as often as I can talk her into making it.
